my_hash_cash_app was written using Python 3.6.9

Use the following commands to run it on Linux:

pip install -r requirements.txt
export FLASK_APP=my_hash_cash_app.py
flask run


Or on Windows:

pip install -r requirements.txt
set FLASK_APP=my_hash_cash_app.py
flask run


To run unit tests use:
python test.py


Use these URLs to verify endpoints using example inputs:

http://127.0.0.1:5000/find?challenge=iBeat&zero_bits=16
http://127.0.0.1:5000/verify?challenge=iBeat&zero_bits=16&proof=62073
